Weight:       10 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         3 hearts, blue blood; changes color in 0.3 seconds; 9 brains

Name:         Mimic Octopus
Scientific:   Thaumoctopus mimicus
Class:        Cephalopoda
Habitat:      Shallow sea
Diet:         Carnivore
